http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/Couple-commits-suicide-in-front-of-train/article13983199.ece

In a shocking incident, a married couple committed suicide by throwing themselves in front of a moving train near Nedumbassery on Tuesday.The deceased were identified as Shibi, 43, a resident of Chowara near here and his wife Joyci, 34. The couple is survived by a 13-year-old son.Investigations revealed that the couple jumped in front of a moving train between 5 and 6.10 a.m.On an alert by locals, police rushed to the spot and recovered the bodies lying on the railway track. Investigations revealed that the couple was going through a financial crisis, which might have forced them to take the extreme step. A case has been registered.